title: Grateful Dead Live at Ventura County Fairgrounds on 1987-06-14
description:

Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree, Tons Of Steel, Ramble On Rose, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues-> Althea, Feel Like A Stranger-> Might As Well
